        "text_block_1": {
            "content": "<p>At Builton, we deliver high-rise condo and office fit-outs—plus residential design-build and renovations—across Metro Manila. We plan around tower rules, permits, and work windows where required, lock scope early, and manage execution under one PM-led team. The result is design-true delivery, admin-compliant execution, and a predictable path from start to handover.</p>\n",
            "regular_weight": false
        },
        "video_block": {
            "video_src": "https://ivory-anteater-144221.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Builton-Prisma.mp4",
            "poster_src": false,
            "aria_label": "Background video"
        },
        "reveal_grid": {
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "title": "Tower-first planning",
                    "content": "<p>We confirm tower rules, permits, work windows, and elevator schedules before mobilizing—so the plan holds in real tower conditions.</p>\n",
                    "image_src": false,
                    "alt": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "title": "Audit before we build",
                    "content": "<p>Our turnover Assurance audit maps defects, admin requirements, and realistic scope, timeline, and budget range—before commitments.</p>\n",
                    "image_src": false,
                    "alt": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "image",
                    "title": "",
                    "content": "",
                    "image_src": "https://ivory-anteater-144221.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Builton-Section-3-02.webp",
                    "alt": "Team member in a hard hat reviewing marble wall slabs with documents"
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "title": "Scope locked early",
                    "content": "<p>Clear decision gates. Variations are documented and approved before work starts, protecting cost and timeline.</p>\n",
                    "image_src": false,
                    "alt": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "image",
                    "title": "",
                    "content": "",
                    "image_src": "https://ivory-anteater-144221.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Builton-Section-3-01.webp",
                    "alt": "Team member in a hard hat working on architectural blueprints at a desk"
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "title": "QA/QC hold points",
                    "content": "<p>Key trades are inspected before they&#8217;re covered. Photos, checklists, and sign-offs keep quality repeatable.</p>\n",
                    "image_src": false,
                    "alt": ""
                },
                {
                    "type": "text",
                    "title": "Handover + aftercare",
                    "content": "<p>Clean punch list, documented turnover, and a 12-month workmanship warranty with scheduled aftercare visits.</p>\n",
                    "image_src": false,
                    "alt": ""
                }
            ]
        },
        "headline_reveal_2": {
            "aria_label": "How we differ",
            "tag": "h2",
            "words": [
                {
                    "text": "HOW"
                },
                {
                    "text": "WE"
                },
                {
                    "text": "DIFFER"
                }
            ]
        },
        "text_block_2": {
            "content": "<p>These 3 outcomes are what we protect on every fit-out — a clear perspective that guides every decision from turnover to handover.</p>\n",
            "regular_weight": false
        },
        "outcome_cards": {
            "items": [
                {
                    "title": "Design-True Delivery",
                    "body": "What you approve is what we build—details locked early, with QA checkpoints that protect the finish.",
                    "number": "01",
                    "image_src": "https://ivory-anteater-144221.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Card-01.webp",
