        "text_block_3": {
            "content": "<p>What sets Builton apart isn&#8217;t just our scope. It&#8217;s how we show up and how we run every project—with disciplined planning, clear communication, and full accountability.</p>\n<p>We define constraints early, lock scope before building, and inspect key trades before they&#8217;re covered. No drama. No surprises. Just a clean handover and dependable aftercare.</p>\n",
            "regular_weight": true
        },
