        "tandem_hub": {
            "heading": "",
            "lead": "<p>Builton accountability means we take full ownership of every project we deliver—no shortcuts, no excuses, just disciplined execution from planning to handover.</p>\n<p>Ownership is a mindset. We define constraints early, align scope before construction begins, and inspect key trades before they&#8217;re covered—so cost, quality, and timeline stay steady from start to finish.</p>\n",
            "bottom_text": "<p>By running design, permits, and build under one PM-led team, we deliver work that is structured, predictable, and built to last.</p>\n",
            "image_src": false,
            "spin_degrees": "720"
        },
